"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-life-style-fashion-team-usa-uniforms-olympics-2024-b2564687.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  'The bottom jacket looks like Ricky Bobby's racing attire in Talladega Nights,' says one person  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 418, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 246, \"end\": 251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Nelson\", \"score\": 0.9961868406241324, \"rank\": 0.00382761614386234, \"text\": \"Ricky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Nelson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Nelson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Ralph Laurenhas unveiledTeam USA's opening and closing ceremony uniforms for the 2024 Olympic and Paralympic Games inParis, France.\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 472, \"end\": 475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998719983238551, \"rank\": 0.0001280063304106308, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 541, \"end\": 557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999917423037803, \"rank\": 5.251337914498271e-06, \"text\": \"Paralympic Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9998170959217714, \"rank\": 0.00016533646620096862, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, some fans believe the uniforms look more like something Will Ferrell's Ricky Bobby would wear inTalladega Nights.\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 655, \"end\": 660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Nelson\", \"score\": 0.9961868406241324, \"rank\": 0.00382761614386234, \"text\": \"Ricky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Nelson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Nelson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Tuesday, June 18, the American designer debuted its red, white, and blue uniforms for this year's summerOlympics- marking Ralph Lauren's ninth time serving as the official outfitter of Team USA.\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 896, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 724, \"end\": 732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997818921781338, \"rank\": 0.000217895362758763, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 824, \"end\": 836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.9591014658921946, \"rank\": 0.04264255197405572, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}, {\"begin\": 887, \"end\": 895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999477322503, \"rank\": 4.790303890440554e-08, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the opening ceremony, which takes place in the French capital on July 26, the fashion brand has dressed US athletes in a classic tailored ensemble.\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 1048, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 948, \"end\": 954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9993787569967495, \"rank\": 0.0004649011833635901, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1005, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999038025932661, \"rank\": 8.409097760706506e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The look features a navy blue, single-breasted wool blazer with red and white tipping and a striped oxford shirt, paired with denim jeans and a suede buck shoe.\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1175, \"end\": 1180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denim\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"denim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denim\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denim\"}, {\"begin\": 1181, \"end\": 1186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"jeans\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the uniforms for the closing ceremony features a more sporty style - a white moto jacket emblazoned with \\\"USA\\\" across it, along with white denim jeans and a Polo shirt underneath.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1355, \"end\": 1366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_Denim\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"white denim\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_Denim\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_Denim\"}, {\"begin\": 1367, \"end\": 1372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"jeans\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeans\"}, {\"begin\": 1379, \"end\": 1389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polo_shirt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Polo shirt\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polo_shirt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polo_shirt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ralph Lauren has once again created designs that not only capture the essence of American style but also embody the spirit and pride of Team USA,\\\" said Sarah Hirshland, US Olympic and Paralympic committee CEO, in a press release.\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1404, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.9591014658921946, \"rank\": 0.04264255197405572, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}, {\"begin\": 1485, \"end\": 1493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997818921781338, \"rank\": 0.000217895362758763, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1540, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999477322503, \"rank\": 4.790303890440554e-08, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1556, \"end\": 1561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah\", \"score\": 0.9809713050346812, \"rank\": 0.018501378508757608, \"text\": \"Sarah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah\"}, {\"begin\": 1573, \"end\": 1575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999038025932661, \"rank\": 8.409097760706506e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As Team USA athletes prepare to represent the United States at the upcoming Olympic and Paralympic Games, this iconic apparel serves as a symbol of unity and inspiration for both our team and the millions of fans who will be cheering them on.\\\"\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1638, \"end\": 1646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999477322503, \"rank\": 4.790303890440554e-08, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1681, \"end\": 1694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999992996891, \"rank\": 6.927104060923533e-10, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Team USA's uniforms have been known toreceive some divided reactionsin years past, as Ralph Lauren unveiled the patriotic looks on Tuesday, it seemed that everyone was pretty much in agreement this time around - that the closing ceremony uniforms appear more fitting for a Nascar race than for the fashion capital of the world.\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 2213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1886, \"end\": 1894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999477322503, \"rank\": 4.790303890440554e-08, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1972, \"end\": 1984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.9591014658921946, \"rank\": 0.04264255197405572, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}, {\"begin\": 2159, \"end\": 2165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASCAR\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nascar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASCAR\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASCAR\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nascar is an Olympic sport now?\\\"\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2216, \"end\": 2222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASCAR\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nascar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASCAR\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASCAR\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"one critic wrote on X, formerly Twitter, in response to Team USA's uniforms.\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2325, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2281, \"end\": 2288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5066300876943777e-21, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}, {\"begin\": 2305, \"end\": 2313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999477322503, \"rank\": 4.790303890440554e-08, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Top looks great, but why did they go full Nascar on the bottom?\\\"\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2370, \"end\": 2376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASCAR\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nascar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASCAR\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASCAR\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"said someone else, referring to the white moto-style jacket.\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Gonna be hot as hell.\\\"\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile onInstagram, one person compared the Ralph Lauren uniforms to Will Ferrell's outlandish Nascar-driving character, Ricky Bobby, in the 2006 comedy filmTalladega Nights.\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2526, \"end\": 2538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.9591014658921946, \"rank\": 0.04264255197405572, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}, {\"begin\": 2551, \"end\": 2563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Will_Ferrell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Will Ferrell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Will_Ferrell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Will_Ferrell\"}, {\"begin\": 2603, \"end\": 2608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Nelson\", \"score\": 0.9961868406241324, \"rank\": 0.00382761614386234, \"text\": \"Ricky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Nelson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Nelson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The bottom jacket looks like Ricky Bobby's racing attire inTalladega Nights,\\\" they said, as another user agreed: \\\"That's EXACTLY what I was thinking.\\\"\", \"from\": 2658, \"to\": 2809, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2688, \"end\": 2693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Nelson\", \"score\": 0.9961868406241324, \"rank\": 0.00382761614386234, \"text\": \"Ricky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Nelson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Nelson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, not everyone believed the uniforms resembled something of a racecar driver.\", \"from\": 2811, \"to\": 2895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, some people offered up other comparisons, like a Nasa astronaut.\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2954, \"end\": 2958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.830961515975735e-16, \"text\": \"Nasa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you have got a business lunch at noon but you are going to space at three,\\\" one person joked on X.\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 3075, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Is the plan to go to the moon after the closing ceremony?\\\"\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"another user quipped.\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3158, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At a preview of the Team USA 2024 collection on Monday, David Lauren - the company's chief branding and innovation officer and its founder's son - spoke toThe Associated Pressabout the fashion brand's \\\"unexpected\\\" yet classic Team USA uniforms.\", \"from\": 3160, \"to\": 3404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3180, \"end\": 3188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999477322503, \"rank\": 4.790303890440554e-08, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3216, \"end\": 3228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\"}, {\"begin\": 3386, \"end\": 3394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999477322503, \"rank\": 4.790303890440554e-08, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We work very closely with Team USA to make the athletes feel at once dressed up, feel like a team, but at the same time comfortable and very distinctively American,\\\" he told theAP.\", \"from\": 3406, \"to\": 3587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3433, \"end\": 3441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999477322503, \"rank\": 4.790303890440554e-08, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nothing says America like blue jeans, especially when we are in Paris.\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3653, \"end\": 3658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.338064587604921e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it gives the athletes a chance to feel a sense of a culture but also feel like themselves and what is natural.\\\"\", \"from\": 3660, \"to\": 3775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lauren also called the closing ceremony looks \\\"more graphic, more fun, a little more exciting.\\\"\", \"from\": 3777, \"to\": 3872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA's polo shirts are made of 100 percent recycled cotton - the first time Ralph Lauren has achieved that level of sustainability in Olympic gear, Lauren said.\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 4038, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3874, \"end\": 3882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999477322503, \"rank\": 4.790303890440554e-08, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3954, \"end\": 3966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.9591014658921946, \"rank\": 0.04264255197405572, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both the opening and closing ceremony uniforms were made and manufactured in the US.\", \"from\": 4039, \"to\": 4123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4120, \"end\": 4122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999038025932661, \"rank\": 8.409097760706506e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ralph Lauren's Team USA opening and closing ceremony uniform apparel, as well as a collection of Team USA apparel and accessories, areavailable to purchaseonline.\", \"from\": 4125, \"to\": 4287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4222, \"end\": 4230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999477322503, \"rank\": 4.790303890440554e-08, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Along with the navy blue blazer ensemble and the white moto-style look, the fashion brand also released a Team USAcolor-blocked baseball jacket, a Team USAgraphic cotton sweater, and several other clothing items.\", \"from\": 4288, \"to\": 4500, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Olympics Gameskicks off in Paris on July 26with an opening ceremony, this time taking place along the river Seine instead of a stadium.\", \"from\": 4502, \"to\": 4646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4538, \"end\": 4543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.338064587604921e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boats for each nation will cross through the center of Paris and finish at the Trocadero - the gardens across from the Eiffel Tower - where the final Olympic traditions will take place.\", \"from\": 4647, \"to\": 4832, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4702, \"end\": 4707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.338064587604921e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The closing ceremony will be held at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 4833, \"to\": 4890, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4874, \"end\": 4889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additional reporting from AP.\", \"from\": 4892, \"to\": 4921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4918, \"end\": 4920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"s